🗂️ Database Schema

Part Table (Inventory)
Field	        Type	    Description
part_id	      String	  Unique Part ID
name	        String	  Part Name
category  	  String	  Mechanical/Electrical/etc
quantity    	Integer	  Available Stock
selling_price	Float	    Selling Price
cost_price  	Float    	Purchase Cost
supplier	    String  	Supplier Name
location	    String	  Storage Location

Transaction Table
Field	          Type	    Description
transaction_id	String  	Unique Transaction ID
part_id	String	Linked    Part ID
type	          String	  SALE / PURCHASE
quantity      	Integer  	Quantity
price	          Float    	Unit Price
date	          Date	    Transaction Date

Customer Table
Field        	Type    	Description
customer_id	  String	Unique Customer ID
name	        String	Customer Name
phone	        String	Contact Number
address	      String	Customer Address

Supplier Table
Field	        Type	  Description
supplier_id	  String	Unique Supplier ID
name	        String	Supplier Name
phone        	String	Contact Number
address	      String	Supplier Address


